    "name": "Cat Me If You Can",
    "steam_appid": 3170490,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cat Me If You Can 将带你进入一个黑白漫画风格的3D世界，处处藏着毛茸茸的惊喜和待解的谜题，等你来探索并沉醉其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170490/extras/f40a655a57b72c6d3f74115e72e27db7.avif?t=1767353190\" width=610 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快扎进这个温馨又迷人的手工世界吧！寻找藏匿在各处的猫咪，用相机捕捉它们的呆萌瞬间。瞪大双眼——只有最敏锐的观察者，才能发现那些藏得最深的“毛绒团子”！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170490/extras/b3efa9804acf642f1f000458c3b7c4f1.poster.avif?t=1767353190\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170490/extras/b3efa9804acf642f1f000458c3b7c4f1.webm?t=1767353190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170490/extras/b3efa9804acf642f1f000458c3b7c4f1.mp4?t=1767353190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170490/extras/4543a204958b314b3fee18211bdd0dca.avif?t=1767353190\" width=610 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想找到所有的猫咪？可没那么简单！它们有些藏在谜题里，有些躲在锁住的门扉或各种奇妙的机关后，等着你去破解。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170490/extras/b99d51f4a38299bf69c280c3290f26ba.poster.avif?t=1767353190\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170490/extras/b99d51f4a38299bf69c280c3290f26ba.webm?t=1767353190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170490/extras/b99d51f4a38299bf69c280c3290f26ba.mp4?t=1767353190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170490/extras/18143163ebbc6c87f47aef7e7261fe52.avif?t=1767353190\" width=610 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在充满魅力与神秘感的独特氛围中，放松身心，开启一段穿越时空的宁静之旅——当然，还有猫咪相伴。从古埃及的阳光沙滩，到日本的温馨小巷，再到中世纪古堡的幽静角落。每一个目的地都值得你驻足细品，仔细探寻，与每一只隐藏的毛球宝贝不期而遇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170490/extras/7bc731cb1b12a0a3701d45836e909636.poster.avif?t=1767353190\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170490/extras/7bc731cb1b12a0a3701d45836e909636.webm?t=1767353190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170490/extras/7bc731cb1b12a0a3701d45836e909636.mp4?t=1767353190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
